OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will start with some
OL,6,Flow cloud, mist and fog patches
OL,7,Faround, though these should lift
OL,8,Freadily during the morning to leave a
OL,9,Fgenerally fine day across the region
OL,10,Fwith sunny spells. Feeling very warm
OL,11,Fin the gentle winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn isolated light shower is
OL,14,Fpossible overnight, chiefly near to
OL,15,Fthe east coast. For most though it
OL,16,Fwill stay dry with clear spells.
OL,17,FPatchy low cloud and fog forming.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
